## Security Review Recommended Before Installing Any External Skill

For skills from the platform market, skillhub, GitHub, or any other external source, it is recommended to load `skill-vetter` and complete a security review before installing.
If the user explicitly confirms they want to proceed without review, skip the vetting step and install directly.

```
read_skills(skill_names=["skill-vetter"])
```

{{ @variable("mcp_notice") }}

